-- Hong Kong Suspends Property From Capital Investment Scheme to Cool Prices
-- B y   N i p a   P i b o o n t a n a s a w a t
-- 2010-10-13T03:36:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/hong-kong-suspends-property-from-capital-investment-scheme-to-cool-prices.html
Hong Kong will temporarily remove
real estate from the investment asset classes under the Capital
Investment Entrant Scheme starting tomorrow, Chief Executive
Donald Tsang said today in his policy address.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
